OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1783705757
OL,3,CFarmer faced with bill of thousands of
OL,4,Cpounds to clear up fly-tipped rubbish
OL,6,FA farmer is facing a bill of thousands
OL,7,Fof pounds to clear up seven mounds of
OL,8,Frubbish dumped on his field on the
OL,9,FBuckinghamshire-Oxfordshire border in
OL,10,FBledlow Ridge.
OL,12,FEvidence suggests the flytippers
OL,13,Fbrought the waste up from London in a
OL,14,Fnumber of lorries and broke down the
OL,15,Ffence to gain access.
OL,17,FThe rubbish includes several fridges,
OL,18,Ffurniture, timber and glass.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
