OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1783705757
OL,3,CFarmer faced with bill of thousands of
OL,4,Cpounds to clear up fly-tipped rubbish
OL,6,FFred Nixey's family have worked this
OL,7,Fland since 1913, but he says business
OL,8,Fis so tough these days that the
OL,9,Fprospect of having to pay out for
OL,10,Funforeseen costs is stressful.
OL,12,FHe says he's had little support from
OL,13,Flocal authorities because the waste
OL,14,Fwas dumped on private land.
OL,16,FBut Mr Nixey's local MP Greg Smith is
OL,17,Ftaking on his case.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
