PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1783705757
OL,3,CFarmer faced with bill of thousands of
OL,4,Cpounds to clear up fly-tipped rubbish
OL,6,FNick Ingram, a resident in the
OL,7,Fvillage, told ITV Meridian: "The
OL,8,Fresponse from the village has been
OL,9,Fgreat.
OL,11,F"You know, we've even had people
OL,12,Foffering to come and load it in the
OL,13,Fvan and take it to the recycling
OL,14,Fcentre, which is not even half a mile
OL,15,Faway.
OL,17,F"Hopefully, we will bring them to
OL,18,FHeel, because that's what needs to
OL,19,Fhappen. That's the only deterrent
OL,20,Fyou've got is to prosecute people."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
