OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1783705757
OL,3,CFarmer faced with bill of thousands of
OL,4,Cpounds to clear up fly-tipped rubbish
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Thames Valley
OL,7,FPolice said: "The Environment Agency
OL,8,Fis responsible for investigating and
OL,9,Fprosecuting offences related to
OL,10,Fenvironmental crime such as this, and
OL,11,Fwe will support them as requested in
OL,12,Ffinding and prosecuting whoever has
OL,13,Fdone this."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/4
